; Coverage test for op.cc O_IF ternary expression evaluation:
; Exercise the ternary operator ? : in expressions.

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Big Purchase
    Expenses:Electronics    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(amount > 0 ? \"positive\" : \"negative\") %(amount)\n"
positive $10.00
negative $-10.00
positive $500.00
negative $-500.00
end test
